{"tid":1618853,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對付港共政府 要用比佢哋更卑劣嘅做法","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:12:13.000Z","uid":213896,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7180cfd3a0c7c611721c9856dc719107ac581e86","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"我爸爸係一個中港車司機佢希望透過依一篇文章俾一個新方向大家<br />\n<br />\n年輕人嘅做法實在太溫和 <br />\n和平嘅抗爭方式只適合係民主嘅社會發生<br />\n但我哋而家對抗緊嘅唔係林鄭唔係警狗<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而係共產黨</span></strong><br />\n做咗咁多年人經常往返大陸同香港 <br />\n爸爸深深地體驗到共產黨嘅人做事可以幾低莊<br />\n所以對付極權<br />\n做事手法要比佢哋更低莊<br />\n每日去同啲狗鬧交 打嘅係消耗戰<br />\n人哋有既係槍 子彈 <br />\n即使係勇武年輕人都唔會夠佢哋嚟<br />\n每晚咁樣只係令更加多嘅人比啲狗拉入去虐待<br />\n<br />\n相反你搗亂福建人嘅麻雀館 民賤聯嘅辦事處<br />\n要嘅時間唔多 但係長久破壞 越破壞越多 <br />\n佢哋就會知驚<br />\n民賤聯就係承傳左共產黨啲揦鮓招<br />\n所以佢地一日唔收皮 民賤聯 福建佬都會繼續惡<br />\n<br />\n對付警狗方面<br />\n依家唔似以前資訊唔發達嘅年代<br />\n爸爸唔明白點解有老豆搵仔呢個咁好嘅平台大家都唔識使用<br />\n大家說好的一世唔原諒警狗呢<br />\n原來只係言語上同佢正面衝突<br />\n你咁樣真係唔會令佢覺得驚<br />\n因為你望住嘅佢哋係全副武裝 有槍<br />\n冠上 &ldquo;合法使用武力&rdquo;之名去&rdquo;執法&rdquo;既狗<br />\n但係放咗工佢哋都有屋企<br />\n爸爸唔明白點解仲未見到狗狗嘅屋企着火<br />\n證明香港人對住警狗仲有一絲憐憫<br />\n對住極權仲會有懦弱嘅心<br />\n與其每日圍狗屋 大家用雷射燈互射 <br />\n時間一到又放催淚彈<br />\n點解唔對準目標<br />\n直搗黃龍 <br />\n<br />\n最後爸爸希望係dark age入面<br />\n大家可以不被捕 <br />\n等啲警狗 民賤聯 藍絲 遭受同我地同樣嘅待遇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><strong><strong>黎明來到 要光復 這香港</strong></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0efb5d417b65c248fd8fa577e6d32b8f37271dbb","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"5e9529088ec551e6f54465590be6d6021584d11a","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e59945cb30344a68c2a2d288e2db2472b2ebd34e","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"62b5572202ab7866f4c503cc0402a799b2bd305b","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8b4ed8e2ead0db365390f9e741a3a759b86f01e1","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fe49de2c69088c01278770d88bec7d377e5dc29d","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"dfa637d069958ddbc4af989f399d64d8680dc191","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:47:49.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"e97dfd6ed48e57132a7754ced2a9527356af37a1","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"5660c0024f82f250a42442eb5a3ac96749951794","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"fb437e8b26a0de1fcff0b38efbbfbab4ff08b72e","tid":1618853,"uid":73694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"搵人捉撚咗林鄭殺咗佢啦<br />\n連登都禁埋 同大陸內聯網有咩分別"},{"pid":"8948a06a1c92c5dd0f510f5d012d17bd4755034f","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7d61e9cc939a1dbfd7b29abb4281a04e67822448","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb437e8b26a0de1fcff0b38efbbfbab4ff08b72e","tid":1618853,"uid":73694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"搵人捉撚咗林鄭殺咗佢啦<br />\n連登都禁埋 同大陸內聯網有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"殺左林鄭 只會有更加多嘅林鄭出現<br />\n要對付嘅係共產黨<br />\n你覺得而家嘅社會真係仲係香港人話緊事?"},{"pid":"7e8ffaf7960117c27fc9b71dcc7cd0be4caa76b5","tid":1618853,"uid":3234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"真真正正要轉地下抗爭了"},{"pid":"06146d59a880581f79e92d06565b69a8bde358b8","tid":1618853,"uid":301384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d02a71e1ffb408c939cbac2f865cd0395fa0bce2","tid":1618853,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:51:41.000Z","msg":"一早講撚左啦 仲咁打戈和理膠"},{"pid":"303fcdc5a0d47b16ec5de6391161a50fe30ca213","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d28d4755a1dff9e1a080a9fdf18c7dc13c84c6a6","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c59ad2e757da33d42000c388a1e2d7e899b9c66e","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab4d271684ae57726ac066409c4cefb3f9da9477","tid":1618853,"uid":260695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dc15eb8e8c92bae300b7849bfd214755c08a09b","tid":1618853,"uid":260695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:18.000Z","msg":"希望應該甘樣做"},{"pid":"2124ffb3fe2d5a1d602617dbff37c2d0c1272edf","tid":1618853,"uid":260695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"香港人，唔可以再對敵人仁慈"},{"pid":"2a23a3f2d926b97a0fac388fda552967002a27f1","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8ffaf7960117c27fc9b71dcc7cd0be4caa76b5","tid":1618853,"uid":3234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"真真正正要轉地下抗爭了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n黑警要死全家 佢哋做嘅所作所為全家都要受返<br />\n爸爸仲話<br />\n既然啲黑警唔怕我哋<br />\n咁應該會怕自己啲子女啦掛<br />\n如果啲仔女受到校園欺凌學都唔夠膽返<br />\n啲大人就會覺得有問題<br />\n香港人唔可以再咁仁慈<br />\n溫和嘅手法只適合用於民主社會<br />\n對於一啲冇良知泯滅人性嘅狗同埋佢嘅後代<br />\n一啲都唔需要憐憫<br />\n所以希望香港人醒覺<br />\n槍口對準黑警後代<br />\n等佢哋話返比佢哋嘅父母知咩叫白色恐怖"},{"pid":"0b53f2b5893767eda733d13514e02d5e0f31cee7","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2124ffb3fe2d5a1d602617dbff37c2d0c1272edf","tid":1618853,"uid":260695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"香港人，唔可以再對敵人仁慈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:35:53.000Z","msg":"冇錯對佢哋仁慈換來嘅只係更加多嘅手足受傷害<br />\n對付港共政權 就要用返共產黨搞我哋嘅低莊方法<br />\n仲要準備長時間抗戰 <br />\n唔好以為咁快可以完結我要佢哋嘅後代<br />\n生生世世都活係恐懼之下"},{"pid":"5fc48e4d9410d8468184349a263f6f988f494145","tid":1618853,"uid":213896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}